article_title: China’s Export Growth Slowed to 11.6% in October
article_text:
BEIJING—China’s export growth slowed in October but was still faster than analysts had expected, providing a rare bright spot for an economy that continues to battle headwinds.

This was tempered, however, by questions about the reliability of recent Chinese trade numbers.
